<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="13Aug1939"><font color="red">13 August 1939</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): Thanks for 2 letters rec&apos;d &hellip; Does the Golf Hotel know anything about F.W. no 1? I hope it is not lost &hellip; We probably go to Bern &hellip; on Monday. (14 August 1939) Please buy the <i>Sunday Times</i> tomorrow. </div>
